# This is the mandox configuration file. It defines the port range that will 
# be scanned on the each host supplied. The format used here is a new-line
# separated list of entries (lines starting with a '#' are ignored),
# each of the following form:
#
# SERVICE:START_PORT-END_PORT
#
# Note that the START_PORT is included and the END_PORT is excluded.
# For example, to scan service ABC on port 8080 you would add the
# following line, here:
# 
# ABC:8080-8081
